&lt;h1 id="the-foundations-are-math-and-logic"&gt;The Foundations Are Math and Logic&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apr 5 2019&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mathematics and logic are the basis for understanding everything else&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Foundational things are principles, they&amp;rsquo;re algorithms, they&amp;rsquo;re deep seated logical understanding where you can defend it or attack it from any angle. And that&amp;rsquo;s why microeconomics is important because macroeconomics is a lot of memorization, a lot of macro bullshit.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>